Package: ReFernment
Type: Package
Title: Automatically Adds RNA Editing Annotations To Plastome Genome Files
Version: 1.0
Date: 2018-05-17
Author: Tanner A Robison
Maintainer: Tanner Robison <robison.tanner@gmail.com>
Description: This package is desigened to ease the process of annotating RNA editing in plastomes in preparation for GenBank submission. ReFernment takes as input a gff, gb, and fasta file for each genome and provides a corrected translation and the appropriate mis_feature annotation in the .gb file. 
License: GPL-3
Imports: Biostrings, ape, stringr, genbankr
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Suggests: knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
